node.text:
Happy Mother’s Day to all mums out there!! 💐💕✨
.
I am usually quite skeptical when a cake or pie looks great. They normally just taste ok 🥱 You know, nothing to shout about. However, I am truly impressed by @elijahpies as this wild berry lavender pie tastes as good as it looks! 👍🏻
.
And yes I have made Dalgona Coffee like finally. 😂 Stay tuned for the video coming right up! 🙊
@dblchin handcrafted! Reminds me of an art! 💙
@happyzboys ahhh got brain fart I mean porcelain
Wow the pie looks like jade!!! Happy Mother’s Day
@tandeminlove happy mama’s day to you too! 💐✨🎊
@avoirlamode awww thank you my dear for the lovely words always! 💙❤️💙❤️
Congratulations dear on this Mother’s Day, I wish the best for you and your beautiful family🌹
Pretty 学姐, Happy Mother's Day! The pie looks so lovely!! 😍
Wow. The pie looks even more yummy in your picture 😋
Yummmy I knew this one would be delish👌🏼❤️
